function popBus(){if(window.__popBus!==undefined)return window.__popBus;try{window.__popBus=("BroadcastChannel" in window)?new BroadcastChannel("pulsePop"):null;}catch(e){window.__popBus=null;}return window.__popBus;}
function popoutNotify(which,open){
  try{var op=window.opener;if(op&&!op.closed){var od=op.document;var cls=(which==="dj")?"dj-out":"comms-out";if(open)od.body.classList.add(cls);else od.body.classList.remove(cls);if(which==="dj"&&open){var dk=od.getElementById("dock");if(dk){try{dk.pause();}catch(e){}}if(typeof op.dstop==="function"){try{op.dstop();}catch(e){}}}if(typeof op.popOpenerRefresh==="function"){try{op.popOpenerRefresh();}catch(e){}}}}catch(e){}
  try{var b=popBus();if(b)b.postMessage({kind:open?"open":"close",which:which});}catch(e){}
}
function popOpenerSync(which,open){try{var cls=(which==="dj")?"dj-out":"comms-out";if(open)document.body.classList.add(cls);else document.body.classList.remove(cls);if(which==="dj"&&open){var dk=document.getElementById("dock");if(dk){try{dk.pause();}catch(e){}}if(typeof dstop==="function"){try{dstop();}catch(e){}}}if(typeof cur!=="undefined"&&cur==="board"&&typeof render==="function"){try{render();}catch(e){}}}catch(e){}}
function popOpenerRefresh(){try{if(typeof cur!=="undefined"&&cur==="board"&&typeof render==="function")render();}catch(e){}}
function popOpenerInit(){if(window.__popOpenerWired)return;window.__popOpenerWired=1;var b=popBus();if(b){try{b.addEventListener("message",function(ev){var d=ev&&ev.data;if(!d||!d.which)return;popOpenerSync(d.which,d.kind==="open");});}catch(e){}}}
function commsOutCard(){return '<div class="commsOutCard"><b>COMMS</b>Comms is open in its own window.<div class="cob" onclick="commsFocus()">&#x29c9; Focus the Comms window</div></div>';}
function commsFocus(){try{var w=(window.__popWin&&window.__popWin.comms);if(w&&!w.closed){w.focus();return;}}catch(e){}document.body.classList.remove("comms-out");try{if(typeof render==="function")render();}catch(e){}}
function POP_MODE(){try{var v=new URLSearchParams(location.search).get("popout");return (v==="dj"||v==="comms")?v:null;}catch(e){return null;}}
function popOut(which){
  if(which!=="dj"&&which!=="comms")return;
  var g={};try{g=JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("pulsePop_"+which)||"{}");}catch(e){}
  var dw=(which==="dj"?360:760),dh=(which==="dj"?660:680);
  var w=g.w||dw,h=g.h||dh;
  var sw=(window.screen&&screen.availWidth)||1280,sh=(window.screen&&screen.availHeight)||800;
  var x=(g.x!=null?g.x:Math.max(0,Math.round((sw-w)/2)));
  var y=(g.y!=null?g.y:Math.max(0,Math.round((sh-h)/2)));
  var feat="popup=yes,width="+w+",height="+h+",left="+x+",top="+y+",menubar=no,toolbar=no,location=no,status=no,scrollbars=yes,resizable=yes";
  var win=window.open("/?popout="+which,"pulsePop_"+which,feat);window.__popWin=window.__popWin||{};window.__popWin[which]=win;
  if(win){try{win.focus();}catch(e){}}else{alert("Your browser blocked the pop-out window. Allow pop-ups for family.clemits.com and try again.");}
}
function popoutApply(){
  var m=POP_MODE();if(!m)return;
  try{document.title=(m==="dj"?"DJ Box":"Comms")+" - Clemit PULSE";}catch(e){}
  window.__gatePassed=true;
  ["pulseEntry","memberGate","loginSplash","splash","splashWrap"].forEach(function(id){var e=document.getElementById(id);if(e&&e.parentNode)e.parentNode.removeChild(e);});
  document.body.classList.add("pop","pop-"+m);try{popoutNotify(m,true);}catch(e){}
  if(m==="comms"){try{cur="board";render();}catch(e){}}
  if(m==="dj"){try{window.__acc={Player:1,Qctl:1,Queue:1};if(typeof _accApply==="function")_accApply();}catch(e){}}
  try{window.addEventListener("beforeunload",function(){try{localStorage.setItem("pulsePop_"+m,JSON.stringify({x:window.screenX,y:window.screenY,w:window.outerWidth,h:window.outerHeight}));}catch(e){}try{popoutNotify(m,false);}catch(e){}});}catch(e){}
}
function dStopBtn(){var d=document.getElementById('dock');try{d.pause();d.currentTime=0;}catch(e){}if(typeof dstop==='function')dstop();if(typeof msSync==='function')msSync();}
function odSync(){var DASH=String.fromCharCode(8212);var dqA=(typeof dq!=='undefined'&&dq)?dq:[];var dqiN=(typeof dqi!=='undefined')?dqi:-1;var nextSong=null;if(dqiN>=0){nextSong=dqA[dqiN+1]||null;}else if(dqA.length){nextSong=dqA[0];}var sEl=document.getElementById('odSong');if(sEl)sEl.textContent=(nextSong&&nextSong.t)?nextSong.t:DASH;var MQ=(typeof window!=='undefined'&&window.MQ)?window.MQ:[];var mEl=document.getElementById('odMovie');if(mEl)mEl.textContent=MQ.length?MQ[0]:DASH;var L=document.getElementById('odList');if(L){var start=(dqiN>=0?dqiN+1:0);var deck=[];for(var i=start;i<dqA.length&&deck.length<6;i++){deck.push(dqA[i]);}if(!deck.length){L.innerHTML='<div class="odempty">Nothing on deck.</div>';}else{var h='';for(var j=0;j<deck.length;j++){var it=deck[j];var ic=(typeof qKindIcon==='function')?qKindIcon(it.k):'';h+='<div class="odi"><span class="odk">'+ic+'</span><span class="odt">'+esc(it.t||'')+'</span></div>';}L.innerHTML=h;}}}
(function(){if(typeof dRender==='function'&&!dRender.__od){var _b=dRender;var w=function(){var r;try{r=_b.apply(this,arguments);}catch(e){}try{odSync();}catch(e){}return r;};w.__od=1;try{dRender=w;}catch(e){}}})();
try{setInterval(function(){try{odSync();}catch(e){}},4000);}catch(e){}
